Phase 20: Data Tables and Forms (v3.0)                     COMPLETE

ARCHITECTURE: Server/Client Split

SERVER-SIDE (BBS Host)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
  Table Flow:
    TableCreate ──► TableAddCol ──► TableAddRow
         │              │               │
         ▼              ▼               ▼
    [position]    [title,width]   TableSetCell
                   [alignment]        │
                                      ▼
                               TableRender ──► [pixel buffer]
                                      │
                               TableScroll (optional)
                                      │
                               TableClear (cleanup)

  Form Definition:
    FormAddField ──► FormBindVar ──► FormRender
     [type,pos]     [-> $VAR$]       [-> pixels]

  Validation:
    FormValidate ──► True/False

  Variable Sync:
    FormSyncToVars   field.Value ──► $VARNAME$
    FormSyncFromVars $VARNAME$  ──► field.Value

CLIENT-SIDE (Terminal/Viewer)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
  Input Flow:
    [keypress] ──► host detects focused field
         │          │
         ▼          ▼
    FormSetValue(Idx, newtext)
         │
         ▼
    FormRender ──► [updated pixel buffer]

  Field Types:
    TEXT     — keyboard input, cursor, MaxLen
    DROPDOWN — click arrow -> expand options -> select
    LISTBOX  — scroll through options, select one
    CHECKBOX — click toggles Value "0"/"1"
    LABEL    — read-only display text

  Focus:
    Tab/Shift-Tab cycles FormFields[].Focused
    Focused field draws highlighted border

✓  Table data structure (rows, columns, types)
✓  Table rendering (grid, headers, cell alignment)
✓  Form fields: text input, dropdown, listbox, checkbox, label
✓  Form validation (Required fields)
✓  Data binding#x2713;  Data binding (FormBindVar ↔ $VARNAME$ text variables)
✓  Scrollable table (TableScroll, ScrollTop, VisRows)

