Codec Directory Structure

img/ — 20 image, animation, and graphics codecs
  jpegdecraw.pas    JPEG decoder (standalone, no pasjpeg dependency)
  gifdecraw.pas     GIF decoder (LZW, animated frames)
  pngdecraw.pas     PNG decoder (deflate, RGBA)
  pngcodec.pas      PNG encoder + decoder
  bmpdec.pas        Windows BMP/DIB (1/4/8/16/24/32-bit, RLE)
  pcxdec.pas        ZSoft PCX (1-8 bit, RLE, 256-color VGA palette)
  tgadec.pas        Targa TGA (8/16/24/32-bit, RLE)
  pbmdec.pas        Netpbm PBM/PGM/PPM (P1-P6 formats)
  icodec.pas        Windows ICO/CUR (RGBA extraction)
  rffdecraw.pas     RFF v2.2 scalable vector font (stroke data)
  grfill.pas        Gradient fills (linear, radial, conical, dithered)
  grfx.pas          Drop shadows, outer glow, box blur
  grbezier.pas      Variable-width Bezier curves (butt/round/square caps)
  grtexmap.pas      Texture mapping on polygons (affine + perspective)
  grclip.pas        Non-rectangular clipping paths (polygon-based)
  gifanim.pas       Animated GIF frame-by-frame playback
  gifinterlace.pas  Interlaced GIF streaming (4-pass)
  jpegprog.pas      Progressive JPEG scan-by-scan streaming
  pnginterlace.pas  Adam7 interlaced PNG streaming (7-pass)
  spriteanim.pas    Sprite sheet animation frame streaming

wav/ — 36 audio, streaming, MP3, MIDI synth, and utility codecs
  wavdec.pas        WAV decoder (PCM, 8/16-bit)
  vocdec.pas        Creative Voice VOC decoder
  mp3dec.pas        MP3 decoder (MPEG-1 Layer III)
  flacdec.pas       FLAC lossless decoder
  aiffdec.pas       Apple AIFF decoder
  audec.pas         Sun/NeXT AU decoder
  adpcmdec.pas      IMA ADPCM decoder
  mididec.pas       MIDI event parser (SMF format)
  midisynth.pas     MIDI FM synthesizer (2-op, 32 voices, OPL2-style)
  midiplay.pas      MIDI tick-by-tick player (bridges parser+synth)
  midistream.pas    MIDI streaming API bridge (audstream callback)
  ansimusic.pas     ANSI music (MF/MB escape sequences)
  moddec.pas        Amiga MOD tracker decoder
  s3mdec.pas        Scream Tracker S3M decoder
  xmdec.pas         FastTracker XM decoder
  pcmdecraw.pas     Raw PCM sample decoder
  pcmdec.pas        PCM format negotiation
  pcmmix.pas        Multi-channel PCM mixer
  wavplay.pas       Hardware audio output
  dosplay.pas       DOS audio output (PC speaker, SB)
  fixedmath.pas     Fixed-point math for DSP
  lzmadecpas.pas    LZMA decompression (pure Pascal)
  dfm2lfm.pas       Delphi DFM to Lazarus LFM converter
  wavstream.pas     WAV chunked streaming decoder
  vocstream.pas     VOC chunked streaming decoder
  modstream.pas     MOD/S3M tick-based streaming mixer
  audstream.pas     Audio streaming API (callback-based framework)
  asyncplay.pas     Cross-platform async audio playback engine
  netaudio.pas      Network audio streaming (TCP/telnet for BBS)
  ringbuf.pas       Lock-free ring buffer (producer/consumer)
  mp3full.pas       MP3 full decode integration
  mp3huff.pas       MP3 Huffman decoding tables (32 tables)
  mp3imdct.pas      MP3 IMDCT frequency-to-time
  mp3requant.pas    MP3 requantization + stereo processing
  mp3synth.pas      MP3 32-point polyphase synthesis filter

prg/ — 6 progressive rendering codecs
  ripdecraw.pas     Incremental RIP stream decoder (cmd-by-cmd)
  ripbindec.pas     Binary scene decoder (compact pre-compiled)
  riptile.pas       Tile-based progressive (64x64 mosaic)
  riplayerdec.pas   Layer-based progressive (bg -> overlays)
  ripchange.pas      Changed-region patches (only sends what changed)
  riprender.pas      Unified progressive renderer (R1-R5 + Phase 23)

pasjpeg/ — 58 JPEG library files (IJG port)

All codecs: {$H-}, pure Pascal, GPLv3, zero external dependencies.
Compile: ppcx64 -Mdelphi -Fuimg -Fuwav -Fuprg -Fupasjpeg rip3api.pas
See CODEC_REFERENCE.md, CODEC_PHASES.md, PROGRESSIVE.md for details.

